{"tid":2454190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(舊聞重貼) 網上調查顯示七成受訪女士曾於港鐵遭遇性暴力，當中最多被觸摸或磨擦身體、其次為被色迷迷注視以及借故挨近等。","createTime":"2021-03-20T04:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T13:50:21.000Z","uid":350584,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b1fcfebcb9a39ab781e7bb14a6f64dbed24b7845","tid":2454190,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:58:19.000Z","msg":"港鐵車廂於繁忙時段極為擠迫，乘客一不留神或會成為性暴力受害者。就讀中五的林同學表示，曾於車廂被人借故挨近並一度觸碰臀部，礙於當時太年幼不懂反應，以為是對方無心之失未有尋助協助。她直斥，港鐵現時支援配套不足，倘於車廂及隱閉地方加裝閉路電視，並加強職員在車廂內巡邏，會更有效打擊性暴力情況。<br />\n<br />\n一項網上調查顯示，七成受訪者稱曾於港鐵範圍遭遇性暴力，當中最多被觸摸或磨擦身體、其次為被色迷迷注視以及借故挨近等。"},{"pid":"fb04b8b6dd46bfe9ed3bb7500babab0f1bdaad01","tid":2454190,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KqXvRuM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKqXvRuM.png&h=d86d664a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"576d02b446c9e8397fa06065391c3b4270191011","tid":2454190,"uid":191453,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJGpbuQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJGpbuQ.gif&h=ccea906c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79d7deb9eeccb8d2399d9ce7f3b626b7a1cc03ef","tid":2454190,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:01:21.000Z","msg":"林同學憶述，就讀小一時與父親搭乘港鐵，車廂環境十分擠迫，被一名男士貼近身體並觸碰臀部及腰部，惟未有理會及尋求協助。現在回想事件，認為倘挺身指正將有阻減低性暴力情況發生。她建議港鐵可於其手機應用程式「MTR Mobile」增設求助熱線，方便乘客遇事時求救。"},{"pid":"c815f5fdd7fed07f4585c0c593a907006ecc59dc","tid":2454190,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"市民林小姐亦分享，數月前一度於港鐵車廂內，有男士以身體某部分貼近她，且持續數分鐘後，她隨即喝止，反被罵「點會掂到你？」幸得身旁數名男士阻止，涉事人方迅速逃去。<br />\n<br />\n林小姐指出，旁觀者目睹事件並喝止極為重要，能起群眾壓力令不法之徒立即收手，亦建議港鐵加裝更多閉路電視。而與其同行的男友人余先生亦指，倘遭非禮必須大聲求助，旁觀者才能出手協助。"},{"pid":"d5601418cef22f5971c1092de24a0462a123ad04","tid":2454190,"uid":1654,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"被色迷迷注視係性暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62967708fee505989dcbae3bfa04bdf016f92881","tid":2454190,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:03:12.000Z","msg":"關注婦女性暴力協會去年6月至今年2月以網上調查訪問419名受訪者，男女分別15%及85%。結果顯示七成人曾於港鐵範圍遭遇性暴力，當中涉及71%受訪者被觸摸或磨擦身體、60.7%被色迷迷注視以及58.7%借故挨近等。惟僅有3位受害人向職員尋求協助，因297位受訪者中，有四成認為職員協助作用不大以及未有見到職員於附近。"},{"pid":"2da66dc28f72b9d9ce00cdbd8b52ea68e0e25bb8","tid":2454190,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5601418cef22f5971c1092de24a0462a123ad04","tid":2454190,"uid":1654,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"被色迷迷注視係性暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5aff8d3ccad646a6a8a450e78e9794e7148f5d","tid":2454190,"uid":54876,"like":0